testcase.title: Upload functionality of Side by Side Viewer

steps.title: the page "Home" should be loaded on log on
I click On "Side by side list" link under "Profile Menu" options on new Home Page
I refresh page
I select the checkbox of "all" report on 'Side By Side Document List' page
I click on 'Delete Item' in 'My Searches and Alerts'

substeps.message: quick search is working as expected

steps.title: I perform Quick Search by "cancer" in new homepage
I select "Regulatory" report type on the Search Results page
I select 5 random reports from 'Regulatory' results page
I click On "Side by side history" link under "Profile Menu" options on new Home Page
I refresh page
I select all the checkbox present under 'Side By Side History'
I click on 'Delete Item' in 'My Searches and Alerts'
I click on 'Side by Side Document Viewer' link on "Side by Side History" page
